name: ViT-TF-Hub-Application
shortDescription: This repositories show how to fine-tune a Vision Transformer model from TensorFlow Hub on the Image Scene Detection dataset.This dataset is the part of the competition which is Mobile AI Workshop @ CVPR 2021.
